The second version of hand-cranked generator MKVI was fully assembled now.
Though it could generally oprate as I initially designed, i t failed to generate enough electricity.
The best result was 8Volts and 200 mA.
To achieve my goal, I need 2 times more output of this.

The 3D model of MKVII is still under construction.
The planetary gear structure might cause friction problems.
But trying it out is the only way to know whether it will happen or not.

Looking back at my journey on 3D printing, I was initially looking for a method to create a pico-hydro power system which can demostrate my concept of CAFit.

However, I discovered that it's not possible to create such system inside my home.
So I changed my goal and started learning more about 3D modeling and tried to make a human powered generator.
Meanwhile, I started discovering 3D printing community on facebook.

Yet neither making a significant human network online nor mastering 3D model designing was not a easy task.

The Judge who organize the oral debate this time was professional enough.
He rejected the illegal proposals from those shameless LAAs in the begining.
But those law thugs still did not give up.
They want to keep frauding people.

Besides consolidating our proposal, wer must prepare ourselves for any kind of dirty tricks played by those thugs.
They are scums who dare to claim fake and illegal proposal in the face of law.
There is a law calld "LAA bill" which regulate those people, but those law thugs absolutely have no intention to obey it and they never got punished by it.

